    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver and it's ready for its next adventure. It's in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super dependable for all my trips. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. I'm looking for a quick sale, so I've set a great price for such a steady ride! Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
