    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a 2011 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen features the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise handling dynamics. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014common S65 failure points\u2014have been proactively replaced. The chassis remains stiff with no subframe issues, though the finish shows minor road rash commensurate with its mileage. It is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Recent service completed. Title in hand.",
