    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality, having been meticulously maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though you will find the occasional minor stone chip on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of careful road use. Step inside to a cabin that remains smoke-free and remarkably fresh; the premium leather seats are supple, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with age. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It comes with a documented service history, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a fresh multi-point inspection. The tires offer excellent tread depth, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. On the road, it tracks perfectly straight and delivers a smooth, quiet ride. This is a reliable, high-quality driver\u2019s car for someone who appreciates a vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
